                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-996" type="given" value="LAURENTIA"></interp>LAURENTIA DIZI</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a teacher of French. The prisoner came to my house on the 6th of June—he said he came to have his little girl taught French—when he was gone I missed a shawl, which had been on a sofa in the room—no one else had been there but Jane Vignette.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
