                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-997" type="given" value="JANE"></interp>JANE VIONETTE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with the prosecutrix. When the prisoner came there was a shawl in the room, on the end of the sofa—it was missed directly he was gone—it must have been taken by him—I met him last Thursday night, at half-past eigth o'clock—he saw me, and ran away—I pursued him, and gave him into custody.</p>
